1. *Špijun* je otkriven na granici. (*Spy* was discovered at the border.)
2. Policija je uhapsila *špijuna* u tajnoj operaciji. (Police arrested a *spy* in a secret operation.)
3. *Špijunska* mreža je bila aktivna tokom rata. (*Spy* network was active during the war.)
4. Njegova misija je da se infiltrira kao *špijun* u neprijateljsku teritoriju. (His mission is to infiltrate as a *spy* into enemy territory.)
5. Vlasti su optužile stranog diplomatu za *špijunažu*. (Authorities accused a foreign diplomat of *espionage*.)
6. *Špijunski* filmovi su popularni žanr u filmskoj industriji. (*Spy* movies are a popular genre in the film industry.)
7. On je bio *špijun* u službi svog državnog aparata. (He was a *spy* in the service of his state apparatus.)
8. Agencija za nacionalnu bezbednost uhvatila je *špijunsku* opremu u njegovom stanu. (National security agency caught *spy* equipment in his apartment.)
9. *Špijunaža* je ozbiljan zločin u mnogim državama. (*Espionage* is a serious crime in many countries.)
10. Otkriveni *špijun* je priznao da je radio za stranu obaveštajnu službu. (The uncovered *spy* admitted he was working for a foreign intelligence service.)